social_posts.post_text: For the latest cover of @nymag, I profiled Donald Trump in his Norma Desmond era. Link in bio.
People are like wHY dOeS dOnAlD tRUmP tAlK 2 yOu as if this is a guy with an otherwise rich history of making rational decisions
They call Los Angeles the City Of Angels. I didn't find it to be that, exactly. But I'll allow there are some nice folks there.

For the latest issue of @nymag, I wrote about @thestormydaniels, perhaps the most burdened woman in America. She is smart and funny and cool and courageous and it’s impossible to not love her. Original 📸 by @barrettblade777 and 🎨 by @zoharlazar. Special thanks to @kathygriffin 🙏

Coming May 1 to @hbo — over five episodes, I’ll be talking to the cast and creators of White House Plumbers to discuss what really happened during Watergate and what is going on with @justintheroux’s mustache. 

Listen on @hbomax or wherever you get your podcasts.

Rudy! A Documusical - coming to a streaming giant near you this summer. Thanks to director @jedrothstein for having me work on this project, and thanks to Rudy for providing us with endless material. Watch on @appletv, @hulu, or in your fever dreams.
